    "This project implements a fun version of the classic Rock-Paper-Scissors game using Python. The game allows the user to play multiple rounds against the computer, with a scoreboard to track wins, losses, and ties. It also includes humorous messages, a dramatic countdown, and a hidden cheat code to enhance engagement.\n"
